column99:
UAB Laivsta is looking for Quality Engineer for ongoing Industrial project in Denmark, Kalundborg: 
 Responsibilities of the role: 
 Perform quality control of steel structures and pipeline products. 
 Check the quality of incoming raw materials and production. 
 Ensure continuous quality control of the production process. 
 Prepare quality management documents, reports - filling out executive documentation. 
 Ensuring work safety, quality, and work efficiency requirements. 
   
 Requirements for the role: 
 You have experience in quality control of metal structures production or pipeline assembly and installation. 
 You are familiar with welding processes. 
 You have a higher technical education. 
 You are familiar with the standards governing the quality requirements of stainless steel welding and assembly of structures. 
 You are fluent in English. 
 You are computer literate (MS Office + MS Project). 
 You have valid VT or PT certificates - an advantage. 
 You have a welding inspector certificate - an advantage.
